{"id":942634363,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"1 month, 1 week","timestamp":1682947487,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"0 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/942634363/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Roman to Integer","memory":"6.1 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int I = 1;\n    int V = 5;\n    int X = 10;\n    int L = 50;\n    int C = 100;\n    int D = 500;\n    int M = 1000;\n    int char_to_int(char c) {\n        switch (c) {\n            case 'I':\n                return 1;\n            case 'V':\n                return 5;\n            case 'X':\n                return 10;\n            case 'L':\n                return 50;\n            case 'C':\n                return 100;\n            case 'D':\n                return 500;\n            case 'M':\n                return 1000;\n            default:\n                return 0;\n        }\n    }\n    int romanToInt(string s) {\n        int res;\n        int max_num = 0;\n        if (s.size() == 0)\n            return 0;\n        if (char_to_int(s[s.size()-1])) {\n            res = char_to_int(s[s.size()-1]);\n            max_num = res;\n        }\n        for (int i = s.size()-2; i >= 0; --i) {\n            int temp = char_to_int(s[i]);\n            if (temp < max_num) {\n                res-=temp;\n                continue;\n            } else {\n                res+=temp;\n                max_num = temp;\n            }\n        }\n        return res;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"roman-to-integer","has_notes":false}
